{"tid":917353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[選後檢討] 梁國雄：焦土派任由暴政取得勝利有如政治自殺！自己諗！","createTime":"2018-11-26T10:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T13:16:50.000Z","uid":49388,"like":6,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c67efccea332d616738ea00ddac01473a5837812","tid":917353,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"梁國雄：其實不太想道歉<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄發言時，則籲民主派不僅要口頭講「團結」，在議會抗爭及社會運動上都要有共同行動。他又坦言自己其實不太想道歉，「你唔投票唔通殺咗你？」他不點名批評「焦土派」，形容任由暴政取得勝利有如「政治自殺」，呼籲各位選民「自己諗」。"},{"pid":"2223390896dcdf84e17228d1a9c66019c8fca469","tid":917353,"uid":11055,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=aa3f7238\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ff5b3de3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=93b29512\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cb113d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=Whuuq17inbS6e5jWNpwJAiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=58d59221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n選你入去即係買兇殺自己？"},{"pid":"2ba6002959172f2220e32c21213c43c859b625ce","tid":917353,"uid":173930,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"我諗得好清楚，下鋪要你班賤人票債票償<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/do